{"tid":2367483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田警署外聲援黃國桐　王婆婆：咁多政治逼害令人好煩惱","createTime":"2021-01-15T11:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T14:05:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f01c819aa5e208094cdd38630ce3365b41ae0835","tid":2367483,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/138218149_3813525962066329_5174836008977454069_n.png?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=0YN0Ij8fz2EAX9TrpdF&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=0611be390dcb2fa74db7a52c2f84f08b&amp;oe=60265BF9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F138218149_3813525962066329_5174836008977454069_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D0YN0Ij8fz2EAX9TrpdF%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D0611be390dcb2fa74db7a52c2f84f08b%26oe%3D60265BF9&h=77fac82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方國安處昨（14 日）早拘捕本身為律師的區議員黃國桐、前學聯副秘書長何潔泓的母親等合共 11 人，指他們涉嫌「協助罪犯」，及後證實與 12 港人案有關。消息指，王國桐料今晚可保釋。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚，王婆婆到沙田警署外聲援黄國桐，擺放「Fight For Freedom」燈箱。她指，原本打算送飯盒入警署，但警員指飯盒食物有骨頭未成事。對於昨日再有 11 人突然被捕，她形容現時「咁多政治逼害令人好煩惱」。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆說，昨晚曾到沙田警署短暫停留，但獲代表律師告知黃未能獲釋，今日不斷緊張地查看新聞，一直留意黄的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3813525958732996/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3813525958732996%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=45bbc8a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3813525958732996/</a>"},{"pid":"3cab7f1895e678d6bcc9809253e3c793cd65aafc","tid":2367483,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441dcd3bb7f3f5827b37746cba28d6b4fb948960","tid":2367483,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5e4bba37ae186a9818be473714190f8ad8f426","tid":2367483,"uid":35296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb76ff7ff1acf773f9c3a0429927be0b88a7d95","tid":2367483,"uid":220985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"黃婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b99f5c8f248defc0b7456e7612d6e85250b6c1a","tid":2367483,"uid":220985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bb76ff7ff1acf773f9c3a0429927be0b88a7d95","tid":2367483,"uid":220985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"黃婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推post"},{"pid":"38463a8265ea0d3785d0207781cdba8a2edaeb63","tid":2367483,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9869f37595d827d7404b28c8e8cdb71575807876","tid":2367483,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-